General.Description: Fable is a Discord Fantasy RPG game developed in 2023 by Lunar, and maintained since 2025 by Jay. It is based off of a now extinct bot called IdleRPG. By using commands, the user can send their character on quests, gamble, join fellow characters in raids, battle each other, and create families. These characters gain experience, loot, money, and weapon crates to level up their character to go on more fierce adventures.

Thief.Special: Access to the $steal command (chance to steal 10% from another player)

Ritualist.Special: Gain additional favor from sacrificing items; twice as likely to receive loot from adventures

Ranger.Special: Access to a $pet that can hunt for weapons

Paladin.Special: Access to the $bless command (grant temporary XP boost to another player)

Reaper.Special: Unlocks Undying Loyalty (ability to cheat death in raid battles)

Santa's Helper.Special: Access to the $gift command (ability to gift a player a random weapon crate)

Godless.Description: Not following a god has constant luck of 1.0

Astraea.Description: The good-aligned Goddess with variable luck

Sepulchure.Description: The evil-aligned God with variable luck

Drakath.Description: The chaos-aligned God with variable luck

SwitchingGods.TokenUsage: Used to change gods or race

ChangeType.Notes: 1h weapons can only change to other 1h types; same for 2h. Modified weapons cannot be sold or traded unless reset with $resetitem.

Merge.Requirement: Two weapons of the same type

Mystery.Contents: Can contain any other crate type

StatPoints.Usage: Allocate to increase damage, defense, or health

Adventures.Description: Complete quests to gain experience, loot, money, and weapon crates.
Adventures.SuccessRate: Influenced by luck (from chosen god and favor)

Mechanics.PlayerDeath: Removes player's attack power from total

BossDefeated.CrateBidding: Survivors bid on boss's crate; highest bid wins
BossDefeated.MoneyReward: Boss's HP * 2, split equally among survivors
BossDefeated.Note: If no one bids, the crate disappears

RegularBattle.Mechanics: Character vs. character until one is defeated

RaidBattle.Mechanics: Possible to trip instead of attack if luck is poor

Horde.Description: Raid battles against characters until defeated

Rewards.Completion: Option to retry with increased difficulty and random rewards

BattleTower.Notes: Players may choose paths for prizes; failure to choose results in loss of prize

GodRaids.Frequency: A couple of times a week
GodRaids.Participation: Only followers of the respective god

Astraea.Name: Champions of Compassion
Astraea.Mechanics: Followers try to heal or help others; continues until one remains

Drakath.Name: Raid the Void
Drakath.Mechanics: Defeat Eclipse the Void Conqueror; ends when boss or followers are defeated

Sepulchure.Name: A Sacred Temple Emerges
Sepulchure.Mechanics: Active raid where followers make moves to complete the ritual; all participants earn money

Slots.Description: Play slots for a chance to win

Flip.Description: Bet on coin flip (heads or tails)

PlayerVersusPlayer.Description: Gamble against other players without a bet cap

Benefits: Gain a portion of partner's adventure winnings

LoveScore.Impact: Affects maximum number of children (10 + (combined lovescore / 250,000))
